    <!-- FAQ Baterías -->
    <div class="pipod-faq-section">
      <h4 class="pipod-faq-title">Preguntas frecuentes sobre baterías</h4>
      <details class="pipod-faq-item">
        <summary>¿Cuánto dura una batería nueva?</summary>
        <p>12-18 meses en uso normal. Si baja antes, te la cambiamos gratis (garantía 12 meses).</p>
      </details>
      <details class="pipod-faq-item">
        <summary>¿Es mejor cambiar batería o comprar nuevo?</summary>
        <p>Cambio de batería te da 2-3 años más de vida útil. Mucho más barato que dispositivo nuevo.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="pipod-faq-item">
        <summary>¿Tienen baterías en stock?</summary>
        <p>Sí. iPhone siempre en sucursal. MacBook 1-2 días. iPad y Watch: 24-48 horas.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="pipod-faq-item">
        <summary>¿Pierdo datos con el cambio?</summary>
        <p>No. No formateamos. Tus datos permanecen intactos.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pipod-baterias-section {
    background-color: #FFFFFF;
    padding: 50px 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pipod-baterias-section {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }
  }

  .pipod-container {
    max-width: 1440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 25px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pipod-container {
      padding: 0 80px;
    }
  }

  .pipod-section-header {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .pipod-section-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pipod-section-title {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }
  }

  .pipod-baterias-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pipod-baterias-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }

  .pipod-battery-card {
    background: #F5F5F5;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    padding: 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .pipod-battery-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .pipod-battery-icon {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #000000;
  }

  .pipod-battery-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
    color: #000000;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .pipod-spec-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .pipod-spec-label {
    font-family: 'PT Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #888;
  }

  .pipod-spec-value {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
  }

  .pipod-express {
    color: #000000 !important;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .pipod-checklist {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .pipod-checklist li {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #000000 !important;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .pipod-battery-note {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #6E6E6E;
    margin: 24px 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .pipod-button-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .pipod-btn-primary {
    background: #1F1F1F;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .pipod-btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(31, 31, 31, 0.3);
  }

  .pipod-btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: #1F1F1F;
    border: 1.5px solid #1F1F1F;
    padding: 12px 26px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .pipod-btn-outline:hover {
    background: #1F1F1F;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .pipod-faq-section {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid #E0E0E0;
  }

  .pipod-faq-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    color: #000000;
  }

  .pipod-faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E0E0E0;
    padding: 20px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .pipod-faq-item summary {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    list-style: none;
    color: #000000;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .pipod-faq-item summary:hover {
    color: #3A506B;
  }

  .pipod-faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .pipod-faq-item p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #6E6E6E;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
